snippet.title: Dagon: Complete Edition - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Nintendo - https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/dagon-complete-edition-switch/
PlayStation - https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10011636
Xbox - https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/dagon-complete-edition/9NP0W1G35CVG/0010

Dagon: Complete Edition launches on October 10, 2024 for Nintendo Switch, PlayStation and Xbox!

Explore the unique works of H. P. Lovecraft via the interactive stories of Dagon: Complete Edition - an extraordinary collection depicting the horrors creeping beneath the waves, festering within delirious minds, and more.

Learn more:
- 100% faithful adaptations of Lovecraft's works brought to life through atmospheric voice acting
- hidden notes containing rare trivia about Lovecraft’s life and his impact on culture
- a brand new, console-exclusive DLC - What The Moon Brings
- compact stories, each suitable for one gaming session
